high_descs: Move a little back and turn to your right and move towards the countertop.
Take the apple in hand from the counter top.
Move to your left towards the sink.
Open the tap and wash the apple in the sink.
Move a little back and then to your right and go near the sink.
Place the apple on the counter top near the sink.
anns.task_desc: Wash the apple in the sink placed in the counter top.

high_descs: Turn right and go straight to the countertop cupboard.
Pick the apple from the table cupboard.
Slightly move left to the sink.
Place the apple in the sink and wash the apple with the tap water.
Pick the apple from the sink and slightly move to left.
Place the apple on the table beside the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place the apple on the table by washing it in the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and walk straight towards the countertop.
Pick up the apple on the counter.
Turn left and walk towards the sink.
Put the apple in the sink, wash the apple and then pick it up.
Turn left, take a step towards the window and then turn right.
Put the washed apple on the counter beside the sink.
anns.task_desc: Wash the apple and put it on the sink.
